Package: fable.timegpt
Title: TimeGPT Modelling Interface for 'fable'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Mitchell",
             family = "O'Hara-Wild",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "mail@mitchelloharawild.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6729-7695")))
Description: Allows TimeGPT forecasts from the Nixtla API to be used in a
  tidy workflow with the modelling interface of 'fabletools'. This extends 
  TimeGPT to provide enhanced model specification and management, performance
  evaluation methods, and model combination tools.
